rt for H.323, VCS, PBX and other legacy voice/video systems Deployment - Get off the ground in minutes with a clear and concise provisioning tool that makes provisioning simple, easy and suitable for all Industry verticals Damaka&apos;s patented Peer-to-Peer architecture allows customers to reduce Total Cost of Ownership (TCO) with fast deployment and minimal maintenance. Amadeo improves organizational efficiency and productivity with secure, streamlined communications across desktop and mobile platforms Latest Tweet Damaka Introduces Amadeo Cloud #UCC Service for Small to Medium Sized Businesses http://t.co/i13jImxJCx #SMB #mobilebiz #VoIP #enterprise3:42 PM Jul 31st Contact Us 2460 N. Central Expressway, Richardson, TX 75080, USA +1 (972) 696 0080 info@amadeocloud.com Follow Us Twitter LinkedIn  2014 Damaka, Inc. All Rights Reserved. Privacy Policy Terms of Use ',' language english espa','About Amadeo','ok',37,37,'',30084,'https://amadeocloud.com/aboutamadeo.php','40294ed05bbda17a5f8c2e0584adb3d9',-1,0,''),(39,'https://amadeocloud.com/acerca.php','',' Language: English Espaol | User Log In | Admin Log In | Register Toggle navigation Amadeo Cloud Product About Amadeo Features Compare Versions Voice Services SIP Trunks Amadeo Numbers Pricing Amadeo UCC Licensing Voice Services Support FAQ Client Download Partners Partner With Us Amadeo Reseller Program Amadeo Agent Program Company About Us Contact Company Home Company About Us About Us Damaka is a technology leader and an innovator in mobile unified communication and collaboration (UCC) providing the best-in-class solution for today&apos;s complex needs of businesses. The company embodies its mantra of communication and collaboration on \"any device, any network, anytime, anywhere\" by providing secure, real-time video calling and collaboration solutions on all major smartphones, tablets and PC/Mac/Linux platforms. Damaka continues to leap forward in evolving Unified Communications and Collaboration (UCC) by delivering Universal UCC with Amadeo. The technology in the Amadeo UCC solution will connect and interoperate with all existing major UC/UCC solutions such as Microsoft Lync, Google Hangouts, Cisco Jabber/WebEx, and IBM Sametime. Damaka&apos;s patented \"managed peer-to-peer SIP\" based software solutions feature SmartShare/TabShare, Parallel Edits, Federated services across Amadeo on-prem and cloud deployments, and Sweeping, which allows users to seamlessly transfer in-progress collaboration sessions to and from various devices including laptops, tablets and smartphones. The Damaka Universal UCC offering provides a unique solution for service providers, enterprises, and small & medium sized businesses to meet their specific needs with respect to telephony, Video, Collaboration and Mobility. Damaka was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Richardson, Texas, USA. Latest Tweet Damaka Introduces Amadeo Cloud #UCC Service for Small to Medium Sized Businesses http://t.co/i13jImxJCx #SMB #mobilebiz #VoIP #enterprise3:42 PM Jul 31st Contact Us 2460 N. Central Expressway, Richardson, TX 75080, USA +1 (972) 696 0080 info@amadeocloud.com Follow Us Twitter LinkedIn  2014 Damaka, Inc. All Rights Reserved. Privacy Policy Terms of Use ',' language english espa','About Amadeo Cloud: The Company','ok',38,38,'',15258,'https://amadeocloud.com/acerca.php','d7db72fe193b38b7a9fa52437c5f801e',-1,0,''),(40,'https://amadeocloud.com/agentsprogram.php','',' Language: English Espaol | User Log In | Admin Log In | Register Toggle navigation Amadeo Cloud Product About Amadeo Features Compare Versions Voice Services SIP Trunks Amadeo Numbers Pricing Amadeo UCC Licensing Voice Services Support FAQ Client Download Partners Partner With Us Amadeo Reseller Program Amadeo Agent Program Company About Us Contact Partners Home Partners Amadeo Agent Program Amadeo Agent Program The Amadeo Agent Program (AAP) is designed to work as a referral program. It allows business professionals to earn extra cash by lev